that burn out

00:02:54.070 --> 00:02:58.760 align:middle line:84%
before the patients that have
the life-threatening illnesses.

00:02:58.760 --> 00:03:01.240 align:middle line:10%
So we have to
remember that and know

00:03:01.240 --> 00:03:03.580 align:middle line:10%
that if you're in the
driver's seat for the moment

00:03:03.580 --> 00:03:07.270 align:middle line:10%
to help someone else, you
can only do it if you're

00:03:07.270 --> 00:03:10.210 align:middle line:10%
taking care of yourself.

00:03:10.210 --> 00:03:12.520 align:middle line:84%
>> Chronic stress
can cause insomnia.

00:03:12.520 --> 00:03:15.290 align:middle line:84%
And lack of sleep
adds to stress.

00:03:15.290 --> 00:03:18.040 align:middle line:84%
How do we break
this vicious cycle?

00:03:18.040 --> 00:03:22.480 align:middle line:84%
>> Insomnia is one of the things
that will really work against

00:03:22.480 --> 00:03:24.610 align:middle line:90%
us in any situation.

00:03:24.610 --> 00:03:28.660 align:middle line:84%
Without sleep, our brain can't
detox, our body can't repair,

00:03:28.660 --> 00:03:31.030 align:middle line:84%
we can't make
hormones, we can't get

00:03:31.030 --> 00:03:34.030 align:middle line:84%
the anti-inflammatory
molecules going,

00:03:34.030 --> 00:03:37.330 align:middle line:90%
we can't repair our own DNA.

00:03:37.330 --> 00:03:40.480 align:middle line:84%
All of that happens when
we're telling our body,

00:03:40.480 --> 00:03:43.780 align:middle line:84%
we don't need to be
in survival mode,

00:03:43.780 --> 00:03:45.550 align:middle line:90%
we're in peaceful safe mode.

00:03:45.550 --> 00:03:48.940 align:middle line:84%
And it's miraculous
what the body can do.

00:03:48.940 --> 00:03:52.810 align:middle line:84%
But we need meditation
time and we need sleep time

00:03:52.810 --> 00:03:55.280 align:middle line:90%
for that to happen.

00:03:55.280 --> 00:03:58.840 align:middle line:84%
>> You don't need a spa
weekend for self care.

00:03:58.840 --> 00:04:03.910 align:middle line:84%
To recharge, sometimes it takes
as little as five minutes.

00:04:03.910 --> 00:04:07.570 align:middle line:84%
>> There are many studies
that prove that listening

00:04:07.570 --> 00:04:11.860 align:middle line:84%
to your favorite music,
taking a walk in nature,

00:04:11.860 --> 00:04:16.959 align:middle line:84%
even carving out five minutes
to really do something that you

00:04:16.959 --> 00:04:21.820 align:middle line:84%
enjoy, if it's meditation, if
it's exercise, whatever it is.

00:04:21.820 --> 00:04:24.400 align:middle line:84%
Maybe you have 30 minutes,
maybe you have an hour,

00:04:24.400 --> 00:04:27.710 align:middle line:84%
but don't think that five
minutes won't do anything

00:04:27.710 --> 00:04:28.510 align:middle line:90%
for you.

00:04:28.510 --> 00:04:30.460 align:middle line:90%
It will, it can.

00:04:30.460 --> 00:04:33.880 align:middle line:84%
Even a couple of
very deep breaths

00:04:33.880 --> 00:04:36.460 align:middle line:84%
can be really
restorative for you.

00:04:36.460 --> 00:04:40.120 align:middle line:84%
And I think when we get
stressed, we forget to breathe.

00:04:40.120 --> 00:04:43.300 align:middle line:84%
>> If it all feels like
too much right now,

00:04:43.300 --> 00:04:47.260 align:middle line:84%
what can one do if we feel
like we are spiraling?

00:04:47.260 --> 00:04:51.760 align:middle line:84%
>> And if you spend more time
in what you can do right now

00:04:51.760 --> 00:04:56.210 align:middle line:84%
instead of what you can't do,
you'll be empowered to say,

00:04:56.210 --> 00:04:59.470 align:middle line:84%
hey, I'm going to come out of
this and I'm and have learned

00:04:59.470 --> 00:05:02.920 align:middle line:84%
something and I'll be a
wiser person because of it.

00:05:02.920 --> 00:05:06.740 align:middle line:90%
And, I'll be stronger.

00:05:06.740 --> 00:05:09.860 align:middle line:84%
>> If you are feeling the
effects of chronic stress,

00:05:09.860 --> 00:05:13.610 align:middle line:84%
remember you must take care
of yourself to be able to care

00:05:13.610 --> 00:05:14.900 align:middle line:90%
for others.

00:05:14.900 --> 00:05:19.100 align:middle line:84%
Even a few minutes of
meditation, yoga or walking

00:05:19.100 --> 00:05:21.800 align:middle line:84%
in nature can help
you reset and be

00:05:21.800 --> 00:05:24.530 align:middle line:84%
ready to face the
challenges ahead.

